      "widgets_values": ["NB2 Tile Upscale - Regenerative 2x2\n\nPipeline: Tile Crop → Extract (×4) → [upscaler per tile] → Tile Collect → Tile Stitch → DPI export.\n\nAs saved, each tile uses Tile Scale By / Placeholder (AM) at 2× as a runnable stand-in.\nOnce the tiling and stitching look correct, replace each TileScaleByAM with your NB2 node.\nThe rest of the workflow stays identical — just swap the node in the middle.\n\ntile_metadata flows: TileCropAM → TileCollectAM (passthrough) → TileStitchAM."]
